== Cultural Properties ==

=== Shiga Prefecture Designated Cultural Properties ===
* '''Scenic Site'''
** '''Karasaki (Karasaki Shrine Grounds)''' – Designated on June 19, 1998 (Heisei 10).<ref>{{PDFlink|[http://www.pref.shiga.lg.jp/edu/katei/bunkazai/bunkazaimokuroku/files/13.pdf Shiga Prefectural List of Historic Sites, Scenic Spots, and Natural Monuments]}} (Shiga Prefecture Official Website).</ref>

=== Ōtsu City Designated Cultural Properties ===
* '''Historic Site'''
** '''Karasaki (Karasaki Shrine Grounds)''' – Designated on January 16, 1981 (Shōwa 56) as a Historic Site and Scenic Spot.<ref>Ōtsu City Board of Education Notification No. 3, January 16, 1981.</ref><ref>On-site explanatory board.</ref>

